name: CageStar Mixed Martial Arts Tee
description:
Skulls, daggers, wings - They may all have their place on MMA Tee's, but not on this one. Simple & to the point - This is mixed Martial Arts.

Screen printed on the finest, high quality 100% cotton it's built to last. All of our printing is done in house here in the UK, not in a sweatshop in China. We are proud of that fact. 

We only use the finest quality screen printing inks, so a soft yet striking print is guaranteed on each and every shirt.

We will be doing a limited run of this ultra exclusive tee. Grab one while you can!

name: CageStar Collegiate Style Tee
description:
Classic Collegiate styling & Uber comfortable - CageStar Athletics  
 
Heather Grey  
90% Super Soft Cotton 
10% Polyester 
100% MMA

We use the best quality shirts money can buy. This means your new tee wont:

A) Shink in the wash
B) Fall apart after you have worn it a few times
C) Do that weird out of shape thing where one sleeve seems to get longer than the other......you know what i mean.

Screen printed using the highest quality water based inks for a soft print effect. None of your iron on rubbish here. 

Designed and printed by us here in the UK. No sweatshops, no delays, no excuses.
